---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<PageLayout title="AJ Markow">
  <div class="about-section">
    <h2 class="about-heading">About Me</h2>
    <p>Hi, my name is AJ Markow, welcome to my coding portfolio. I'm currently working at Recharge, the leading subscription software as a service. I've loved working with computers since I built my first Geocities site, and I'm fortunate to now do it for a living.</p>
    <h2 class="about-heading">Languages & Tools</h2>
    <ul class="about-list">
      <li>JavaScript</li>
      <li>Node.js</li>
      <li>HTML & CSS</li>
      <li>Ruby</li>
      <li>Ruby on Rails</li>
      <li>React</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="about-heading">Certifications</h2>
    <ul class="about-list single">
      <li>AWS Cloud Practitioner</li>
      <li>Salesforce Administrator</li>
      <li>Shopify Foundations</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
